    "long_instructions": "## Try Your Own\r\n\r\nPractice asking the same question in different ways.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Reflect on these two questions.\r\n\t* How does the way we phrase a prompt influence AI contradictions?\r\n    * Why does AI provide inconsistent responses even when asked the same question differently?\r\n2. Now **try out your own example of a question**. Frame it in as many ways possible to see if you can produce contradictions in the AI responses.",
